  @condibear n est pas vantard. Il vit sa vie de fa on modeste et respecte ceux qui l entourent. C est ce qui le d marque. Ensuite, il a gradu  d une  cole de l Ivy League en venant d une famille de classe moyenne. Je suis fier de voir qu il est humble et qu il est devenu la personne qu il est. C est un bon gar on. Quand il a sign  son premier contrat, il a achet  des gants   l quipe de son  cole secondaire, Belmont Hill. Je crois qu il comprend. Il veut faire le bien autour de lui. Je suis tr s fier de lui.  
- Ted Condon   propos de son fils, Mike
 @condibear isn t a bragger. I think he goes about life modestly and with respect for other people. I think that really stands out. Then, there s graduating from an Ivy League school coming from a middle-class background. I m proud that he s humble and that he s the person that he is. He s a good kid. When he signed his first contract, he bought the team at [his former high school] Belmont Hill some gloves. I think he gets it. He s good to other people. I m very proud of him. 
- Ted Condon on his son, Mike

  @bgally.11 adore jouer. C est vraiment beau de voir quelqu un qui aime autant le sport et tout ce qui s y rattache. J ai toujours aim  le voir faire des choses qu il appr cie. C est tr s sp cial de le voir aller. Pour nous, de le voir prendre de la maturit  en tant que joueur et obtenir plus de responsabilit s   et m me d aider le d veloppement d'autres joueurs en m me temps  , c est tout ce que j aurais pu demander.  
- Ian Gallagher   propos de son fils, Brendan
 @bgally.11 really loves to play, and it s really nice watching somebody who truly loves the sport and loves everything about it. I think it s always been a similar enjoyment in watching him do something that he loves to do. It s pretty special to watch. For us, to watch him grow as a player and take on more and more responsibility   and actually support the development of others along the way   it s been everything you could ask for. 
- Ian Gallagher on his son, Brendan

